fields.title: Roast Fish 烤鱼
fields.description:
Good for 4 people. Roast fish is served with a pot that will cook with fire. You can choose different type of fish and vegitable. Price varies accordingly.

Please contact me if more people will be included.(Mail address in home page)

 

Main Ingredients

Fish
Vegitables(Potato, lettuce, etc)

 

Origin and Story

Roast fish is originally from Chongqing, China, which is also my hometown. Chongqing is very rish in fishes so we have large variety of fish dishes. Roast fish is one of the most famous party serving, no matter in winter or summer.

Fish will be gilled first then braised  in a soupe together with all types of fresh vegitables.  The flavor of fish goes into soupe, then into vegitables, which taste very fantastic. It is also my husband favorite dish back in China. You should not miss it.

Here is a guide of trying out roast fish in Beijing( if you have a plan to travel there):

 

Try Roast Fish in Beijing

Braised Chicken / 黄焖鸡(Huang Men Ji)
fields.description:
Free Rice will be offered!

Note: Chicken bone will be removed before cookin,  to better suit French dining habit.

Main Ingredients

Chicken 
Bell pepper
Soy sauce
Oyster sauce

 

 

Origin and Story

This is the dish I can eat everyday for one whole month!  In Beijing, there must be one restaurant who is selling and only selling this dish, every 2 kilometers!

 It is originally from Shandong Province, which is located east of China. The attractive feature about this dish is that, chicken leg becomes even softer and super tasty.  The combination of pepper , oyster oil and soy sauce flavor will keep asking you for a second taste.
